n\", \"Option2 Value\": \"5 Sealed Burners + Griddle\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - Professional Plus II Gas Cooktops - UHCPT95FSSLP\", \"Variant Inventory Tracker\": \"shopify\", \"Variant Inventory Qty\": \"10\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UHCPT95FSSLP\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UHCPT95FSSLP_p136433-1.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UHCPT95FSSLP_p136433-1.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"2499.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202334525\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \"      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"product-desc\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>ILVE 36\\u2033 Built-In Gas Cooktop with 5 Burners, in Stainless Steel</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The irresistible appeal of technology and performance.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">AISI304 steel \\u2013 the raw material par excellence used in the kitchens of the best restaurants \\u2013 is the emblem of Professional Plus. A complete system of range cookers, cooktops(hobs) and hoods to design and enjoy top performances in the kitchen. Aesthetics that reflects the topmost professionalism, tailored to the space of the home.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><ul style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><li>Dual gas burner</li><li>Sturdy cast iron pan grates</li><li>Safety valve</li><li>Total Black brass burner with non-stick nanotechnological coating</li><li>Electric ignition\\u00a0Integrated in the knobs</li><li>Continuously adjustable flame</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Professional Knobs: Visibly Functional.</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Created exclusively for Professional Plus range cookers, knobs are made entirely of aluminum with an oversized diameter. Stemming from the experience in professional kitchens, they can be easily used even with gloves and have particularly clear and legible graphics.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Total Black Brass Burner\\u00a0with Non-Stick Nanotechnological Coating</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The noble technical characteristics of brass are enriched with a nanotechnological coating that assures easy cleaning, with an elegant Total Black finish.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Cast Iron Pan Supports</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The indestructible cast iron pan supports provide a functional and safe support for the pots.</p><p></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>California Proposition 65</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">WARNING: Cancer and Reproductive Harm</p><p><a href=\\\"http://www.P65Warnings.ca.gov\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">www.P65Warnings.ca.gov</a></p></div>.<br><br><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br><br></div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" data-slug=\\\"accessories\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Accessories</span> </span></h3>      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">                     </div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_videos\\\" class=\\\"station-